=== bing_daily_pics

I wanted a way to help me download the Bing pics of the day from the homepage (bing.com).

It relies on the following rss feed : http://feeds.feedburner.com/bingimages

==== To get started

gem install ruby-growl
chmod +x bing_1.rb

Edit the script to your liking

./bing_1.rb


=== Notes

* I've only test on Mac OSX Lion
* I've only tested on ruby 1.9.2 p290